#### PR description:

Title says it all, additionally a few minor fixes are introduced:
  * configuration file for unit test in  `Alignment/MillePedeAlignmentAlgorithm/` which was leading to apparently uncaught exception in the [tests](https://cmssdt.cern.ch/SDT/cgi-bin/logreader/slc7_amd64_gcc820/CMSSW_11_1_X_2020-01-14-2300/unitTestLogs/Alignment/MillePedeAlignmentAlgorithm#/);
  * update the example `ini` file to comply with current standard;
  * indentation in the validation script;
  * support again the `dryRun` mode which was removed in latest iteration.

#### PR validation:

Relies on existing unit tests and the one added in this PR.

#### if this PR is a backport please specify the original PR:

Not a backport.
